en-US.summary: Kick your indoor training planning up a notch. Quickly find out what guest worlds are active and when your favorites are up next.
examplePhrases: Alexa, ask Which World, where can I ride today?
Alexa, ask Which World, what guest world is next?
Alexa, ask Which World, when can I run in London?
en-US.name: Guest World Calendar
en-US.description: This skill assists indoor cycling and running enthusiasts with a convenient way to learn what guest world is currently available in an online virtual training game. This skill does not require an account or special hardware.
